These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, february, november, october
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, poppy, zinnia, lily
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, coffee, almond-milk, fanta
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, skateboard, snowmobile, car
1. the person who growspoppy is the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who growsrose##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
5. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
6. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person who growspoppy is the person driving the trike##1
8. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Birthday         | july  | october  | february | november |
| Flower           | poppy | rose | lily  | zinnia  |
| Beverage   | fanta       | almond-milk      | juice | coffee      |
| Transport           | trike          | skateboard     | snowmobile    | car     |

