.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, quad-bike, snowmobile, airplane
There are 4 different nationalities: american, russian, colombian, japanese
House: wooden, farmhouse, cape-cod, ranch-style
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, techno, r&b, electronic
 1. the person driving the airplane is the fan of electronic##1
 2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far right##1
 3. the cape-cod house is on the far right##1
 4. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 5. the person driving the van is on the right of the wooden house##1
 6. the wooden house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
 7. the farmhouse house is on the right of the russian##1
 8. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the american##1
 9. the person driving the van is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
10. the person driving the snowmobile is the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Transport      | quad-bike | van       | airplane        | snowmobile        |
| Nationality           | russian   | colombian | american   | japanese |
| House   | wooden     | farmhouse    | ranch-style | cape-cod        |
| Music-Genre           | r&b         | folk  | electronic       | techno         |

