.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
House: art-deco, gothic-revival, futuristic, modern
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, february, april, september
4 different games are played: domino, billiard, mah-jongg, bridge
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, airplane, taxi, tram
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the art-deco house##1
2. the futuristic house is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
4. the modern house is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
7. the modern house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
8. the person playing domino is on the far right##1
9. the person driving the taxi is the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| House           | gothic-revival   | art-deco  | modern | futuristic |
| Birthday   | april | september       | february       | june     |
| Game   | mah-jongg       | bridge    | billiard     | domino  |
| Transport           | airplane     | taxi | tram     | helicopter         |

