.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, purple, turquise, brown
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, pall-mall, dunhill, montecristo
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, salsa, dubstep, hip-hop
4 different pets are kept: cat, goat, hedgehog, goldfish
1. the dunhill-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who likes red##1
3. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
4. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of folk##1
5. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
6. the owner of the goldfish is the fan of dubstep##1
7. the fan of folk is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
8. the person who likes purple is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
9. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Color           | red  | turquise    | purple | brown |
| Cigar   | dunhill      | pall-mall    | tiparillo         | montecristo    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa   | folk     | dubstep          | hip-hop      |
| Pet         | goat | cat | goldfish      | hedgehog      |

