.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, march, november, february
City: hamburg, edinburgh, liverpool, marseilles
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, skateboard, jet-ski, helicopter
4 different games are played: whist, domino, scrabble, snooker
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is the person driving the airplane##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is the person driving the skateboard##1
 3. the person traveling to hamburg is the person driving the airplane##1
 4. the person playing scrabble is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is the person traveling to marseilles##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 8. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 9. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1
10. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Birthday          | august  | february | november     | march |
| City           | liverpool  | marseilles      | hamburg | edinburgh    |
| Transport   | skateboard | jet-ski  | airplane    | helicopter  |
| Game           | scrabble   | snooker       | whist       | domino      |

