.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, reggae, r&b, d&b
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, weightlifting, swimming, rowing
House: tower, victorian, colonial, gothic-revival
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, nigerian, brazilian, egyptian
 1. the tower house is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 2. the egyptian is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
 3. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 4. the victorian house is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
 6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 7. the tower house is the brazilian##1
 8. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1
 9. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
10. the mexican is on the left of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre    | jazz | reggae     | r&b    | d&b |
| Sport       | skiing | swimming    | rowing | weightlifting |
| House         | victorian   | colonial  | gothic-revival        | tower    |
| Nationality   | egyptian   | nigerian | mexican    | brazilian |

