3. the thai is on the left of the spanish##1
4. the palace house is on the left of the fan of classical##1
5. the indian is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
6. the thai is on the right of the fan of country##1
7. the ranch-style house is the fan of country##1
8. the fan of disco is the owner of the goat##1
9. the fan of trance is the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Pet      | hedgehog      | goat         | guinea-pig        | bird      |
| House           | ranch-style | palace | farmhouse  | futuristic  |
| Nationality   | indian    | thai     | spanish | malaysian     |
| Music-Genre     | country        | disco     | classical     | trance |

