.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-9::.
House: ranch-style, colonial, craftsman, cottage
There 4 different types of food: potato, grapefruit, pepper, lime
City: boston, new-york, san-francisco, liverpool
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, family, mystery, comedy
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1
2. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
3. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the craftsman house##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is the cottage house##1
7. the person watching mystery movies is the person traveling to boston##1
8. the person eating pepper is on the far left##1
9. the person eating lime is the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| House         | colonial | cottage | craftsman | ranch-style     |
| Food   | pepper   | lime       | potato       | grapefruit  |
| City           | liverpool    | new-york    | san-francisco       | boston       |
| Movie-Genre     | sports     | comedy        | family   | mystery |

