5. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person driving the van##1
6. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the electrician##1
7. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
8. the person watching musical movies is the person traveling to nizza##1
9. the person driving the car is on the right of the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |      4      |
| City      | london     | nizza           | hannover    | colone    |
| Movie-Genre         | action  | musical | satire  | scientific |
