.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-11::.
4 different games are played: billiard, scrabble, domino, monopoly
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, aconite, daffodil, poppy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, skateboarding, skiing, basketball
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, azure, emerald, grey
1. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who likes azure##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
4. the person playing domino is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
6. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
7. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
8. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1
9. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Game          | billiard | domino     | scrabble       | monopoly |
| Flower   | daffodil      | aconite      | poppy     | bellflower   |
| Sport   | skiing   | snowboarding | skateboarding | basketball |
| Color     | emerald    | purple       | azure    | grey     |

