The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, electronic, ambient, salsa
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, orange, brown, light-blue
4 different pets are kept: ferret, dog, frog, goat
 1. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
 2. the fan of ambient is the pall-mall-smoker##1
 3. the owner of the ferret is the chaman-smoker##1
 4. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
 5. the game-smoker is on the far left##1
 6. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 7. the person who likes brown is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of d&b is the owner of the frog##1
 9. the blend-smoker is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
10. the owner of the goat is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |        3        |      4      |
| Cigar       | game     | pall-mall    | chaman         | blend  |
| Music-Genre         | d&b | ambient | salsa | electronic |
| Color       | orange    | amber     | light-blue          | brown      |
| Pet   | frog  | dog    | ferret      | goat       |

